data.description:
Severna Park Schools! Walking distance to SPMS with Oak Hill being the feeder school. Blocks from Kinder Park, B&A Trail, and Severna Park Taphouse. Newly remodeled kitchen with granite counters. The top floor (bi-level) has the kitchen, living room, master bedroom, two additional bedrooms, and a 2nd full bath. Master has attached bath with separate shower and soaking tub. Downstairs has a huge family room, a 4th bedroom, and a 3rd full bathroom along with the garage. Owner recently vacated the property and is being prepared for move-in. Available Dec 1. Up to two pets are allowed (with an additional deposit).

Renter is responsible for all utilities. Up to two animals are allowed. No smoking allowed. Reusable tenant screening reports are not accepted.
